Join the Hoochies of Houston at Road to Essence Stop in Houston, TX. This gathering brings together culture, connection, and resources ahead of the Essence Fest in NOLA. Be sure to stop by the Hoochies of Houston table to pick up Plan C materials, abortion pills by mail resources, and free mini swag, and connect with advocates working to ensure trusted reproductive health information reaches the people who need it most.
